var e=`更新`,t=`Server`,n=`spacing`,r=`随机主题`,i=`转变`,a=`Size`,o=`day`,s=`hour`,c=`min`,l=`sec`,u=`Use`,d=`copied`,f=`copy`,p=`close`,m=`and`,h=`Resources`,g=`Solution`,_=`Providing`,v=`context`,y=`It`,b=`Introducing`,x=`variants`,S=`variables`,C=`Examples`,w=`已读取`,T=`已跳过`,E=`截图`,D=`提示词`,O=`必需`,k=`架构`,A=`GitMCP`,j={Updates:e,"install-step-1":`将 daisyUI 作为 Node 包安装`,"install-step-2":`在您的 app.css 文件中添加 daisyUI 的指令`,Server:t,"UI blocks":`UI blocks`,spacing:n,"available-on":`获取渠道`,"All radio inputs with the same name work together and only one of them can be open at a time. If you have more than one set of accordion items on a page, use different names for the radio inputs on each set.":`所有同名的单选框（radio）协同工作，一次只能展开一个。如果页面上有多个手风琴组件，请为每组手风琴中的单选框使用不同的 name 属性。`,"How to use daisyUI colors?":`如何使用 daisyUI 的颜色？`,"daisyUI is fully themeable and colorable,":`daisyUI 是完全可主题化和可着色的，`,"How to use daisyUI themes?":`如何使用 daisyUI 主题？`,Randomize:r,"try-online":`在线试用`,"2. Get daisyUI bundled JS file":`2. 获取 daisyUI 打包后的 JS 文件`,"Add daisyUI in your CSS file":`在您的 CSS 文件中添加 daisyUI`,"noise background of the button if enabled":`启用时按钮的噪点背景`,"2. Pikaday Calendar":`2. Pikaday 日历`,"Pikaday CDN Example":`Pikaday CDN 示例`,"Pikaday Svelte Example":`Pikaday Svelte 示例`,"Pikaday Vue Example":`Pikaday Vue 示例`,"Pikaday React Example":`Pikaday React 示例`,"3. React Day Picker calendar":`3. React Day Picker 日历`,"There are 3 methods to use modals":`有 3 种方法可以使用对话框`,"Method 2. checkbox":`方法 2. 复选框`,"Method 3. using anchor links":`方法 3. 使用锚链接`,"Follow [Tailwind CSS guide](https://tailwindcss.com/blog/standalone-cli) and get the latest version of Tailwind CSS executable.":`遵循 [Tailwind CSS 指南](https://tailwindcss.com/blog/standalone-cli) 并获取最新版本的 Tailwind CSS 可执行文件。`,"If you are using a prefix for daisyUI, these CSS variables will be prefixed with that prefix as well. For example if prefix is `daisy-`, The  `--alert-color` CSS variable will be `--daisy-alert-color`.":"如果您为 daisyUI 使用了前缀，这些 CSS 变量也会加上该前缀。例如，如果前缀是 `daisy-`，那么 `--alert-color` CSS 变量将变为 `--daisy-alert-color`。","Here's how to use daisyUI llms.txt in your code editor:":`以下是如何在您的代码编辑器中使用 daisyUI llms.txt：`,"Copilot can generate daisyUI code for you.":`Copilot 可以为您生成 daisyUI 代码。`,"Add daisyUI's llms.txt file to your repo so that Copilot can use it by default.":`将 daisyUI 的 llms.txt 文件添加到您的仓库中，以便 Copilot 默认使用它。`,"Run this command to save the llms.txt file to `.vscode/daisyui.md`":"运行此命令将 llms.txt 文件保存到 `.vscode/daisyui.md`","In `.vscode/settings.json` Add this:":"在 `.vscode/settings.json` 中添加：","Now in chat window you can type `@daisyui` to provide daisyUI docs to Cursor.":"现在，在聊天窗口中，您可以输入 `@daisyui` 来向 Cursor 提供 daisyUI 文档。","[popover API and anchor positioning `new`](#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning)":"[Popover API 和锚点定位 `new`](#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning)","CSS Anchor Positioning is a new standard but isn't yet supported in Firefox and Safari ([caniuse.com](https://caniuse.com/css-anchor-positioning)).":`CSS 锚点定位是一个新标准，但尚未在 Firefox 和 Safari 中得到支持 ([caniuse.com](https://caniuse.com/css-anchor-positioning))。`,"In those browsers, the dropdown will appear centered like a modal.":`在这些浏览器中，下拉菜单将像对话框一样居中显示。`,"There's also [this polyfill](https://github.com/oddbird/css-anchor-positioning) that can be helpful.":`还有一个[ polyfill ](https://github.com/oddbird/css-anchor-positioning)可能会有帮助。`,"[Pikaday](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday) - Works everywhere":`[Pikaday](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday) - 随处可用`,"Pikaday is a JS datepicker library and you can use it from CDN or as a JS dependency [Read the docs](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday)":`Pikaday 是一个 JS 日期选择器库，您可以通过 CDN 或作为 JS 依赖项使用它。[阅读文档](https://github.com/Pikaday/Pikaday)`,"you need to change the span text and the `--value` CSS variable using JS. Value must be a number between 0 and 99.":"您需要使用 JS 更改 span 文本和 `--value` CSS 变量。值必须是 0 到 99 之间的数字。","Accordion uses the same style as the [collapse component](/components/collapse/) but it works with radio inputs. You can control which item to be open by checking/unchecking the hidden radio input.":`手风琴使用与[折叠组件](/components/collapse/)相同的样式，但它与单选框输入配合使用。您可以通过选中/取消选中隐藏的单选框来控制哪个项目是打开的。`,"It needs JS to open but it has better accessibility and we can close it using `Esc` key":"它需要 JS 才能打开，但具有更好的可访问性，并且我们可以使用 `Esc` 键关闭它","[Using checkbox](#method-2-checkbox)":`[使用复选框](#method-2-checkbox)`,"`EMAIL`: Your email address":"`EMAIL`：您的电子邮件地址","`FIGMA`: Your Figma API key (optional)":"`FIGMA`：您的 Figma API 密钥（可选）","`LICENSE`: Your Blueprint license key":"`LICENSE`：您的蓝图许可证密钥","← Go back to daisyui.com":`← 返回 daisyui.com`,'<a href="/blueprint/">Blueprint</a>: The Official MCP server from daisyUI (Recommended for best results)':`<a href="/blueprint/">Blueprint</a>：来自 daisyUI 的官方 MCP 服务器（推荐以获得最佳结果）`,'<a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP guides →</a>':`<a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP 指南 →</a>`,'<a href="/docs/skill/">Skill guides →</a>':`<a href="/docs/skill/">技能指南 →</a>`,'<a href="#method-1-details-and-summary">details and summary elements</a>':`<a href="#method-1-details-and-summary">详细信息和摘要元素</a>`,'<a href="#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning-new">popover API and anchor positioning <code>new</code></a>':`<a href="#method-2-popover-api-and-anchor-positioning-new">弹出窗口 API 和锚点定位<code>new</code></a>`,'<a href="#method-3-css-focus">CSS focus</a>':`<a href="#method-3-css-focus">CSS 焦点</a>`,'<a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a>: Free 3rd party MCP server':`<a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a>：免费的第 3 方 MCP 服务器`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Visit daisyUI</a>':`<a href="https://daisyui.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">访问 daisyUI</a>`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Add the themes you want</a>':`<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">添加您想要的主题</a>`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyui.com/llms.txt</a> file is a compact, text version of daisyUI docs to help AI generate accurate daisyUI code based on your prompt.':`<a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyui.com/llms.txt</a> 文件是 daisyUI 文档的紧凑文本版本，可帮助 AI 根据您的提示生成准确的 daisyUI 代码。`,'<a href="https://daisyui.com/SKILL.md" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI skill</a> is a compact, markdown version of daisyUI docs to help AI generate accurate daisyUI code based on your prompt.':`<a href="https://daisyui.com/SKILL.md" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI Skill</a> 是 daisyUI 文档的紧凑 Markdown 版本，可帮助 AI 根据您的提示生成准确的 daisyUI 代码。`,'<a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">React Day picker</a> - React only':`<a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">React Day 选择器</a> - 仅 React`,'<a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Vanilla Calendar Pro</a> - Works everywhere':`<a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Vanilla Calendar Pro</a> - 随处可用`,'<a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Cally web component</a> - Works everywhere':`<a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Cally web Component</a> - 随处可用`,'<a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a>: Free 3rd party MCP server':`<a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a>：免费的第 3 方 MCP 服务器`,'<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex-basis" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Layout</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/width" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Sizing</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Flexbox</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/grid-template-columns" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Grid</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/justify-content" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Box alignment</a>, <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/padding" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Spacing</a>':`<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex-basis" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">布局</a>、<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/width" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">大小调整</a>、<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/flex" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Flexbox</a>、<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/grid-template-columns" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">网格</a>、<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/justify-content" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">框对齐</a>、<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/padding" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">间距</a>`,'<a href="svelte:head">svelte:head</a>':`<a href="svelte:head">svelte:head</a>`,"✅ Correct usage:":`✅ 正确用法：`,"✅ Correct: `daisyUI`":"✅ 正确：`daisyUI`","❌ Incorrect usage:":`❌ 错误用法：`,"❌ Incorrect: `DaisyUI`, `Daisy UI`, `daisy ui`, `DaisyUi`":"❌ 错误：`DaisyUI`、`Daisy UI`、`daisy ui`、`DaisyUi`",'Accordion uses the same style as the <a href="/components/collapse/">collapse component</a> but it works with radio inputs or details elements. You can control which item to be open by checking/unchecking the hidden radio input or setting the open attribute on details element.':`Accordion 使用与 <a href="/components/collapse/">Collapse Component</a> 相同的样式，但它适用于 Radio 输入或详细信息元素。您可以通过选中/取消选中隐藏的 Radio 输入或在详细信息元素上设置打开属性来控制要打开的项目。`,"Add this configuration and set your `LICENSE`, `EMAIL`, and optional `FIGMA` variables.":"添加此配置并设置`LICENSE`、`EMAIL`和可选的`FIGMA`变量。","Add this configuration and set your licensing environment variables.":`添加此配置并设置您的许可环境变量。`,"Add this configuration block and set your license details.":`添加此配置块并设置您的许可证详细信息。`,"Add this configuration to `cline_mcp_settings.json`.":"将此配置添加到`cline_mcp_settings.json`。","Add this configuration to `mcp_config.json`.":"将此配置添加到`mcp_config.json`。","Add this to `claude_desktop_config.json`.":"将其添加到`claude_desktop_config.json`。","After configuring the server, tell the AI model to":`配置服务器后，告诉AI模型`,'Also see <a href="/components/accordion/">accordion</a> examples':`另请参阅<a href="/components/accordion/">手风琴</a>示例`,'As long as you use <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI colors</a> they will work on all themes, light or dark.':`只要您使用 <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI 颜色</a>，它们就适用于所有主题，无论是浅色还是深色。`,'Blueprint is the official MCP server for daisyUI. <a href="/blueprint/">Read more about Blueprint</a>.':`Blueprint 是 daisyUI 的官方 MCP 服务器。 <a href="/blueprint/">了解有关蓝图的更多信息</a>。`,"Brand agreement":`品牌协议`,'Cally is a web component calendar and it works everywhere. <a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read the docs</a>':`Cally 是一个网络 Component Calendar，它可以在任何地方使用。 <a href="https://github.com/WickyNilliams/cally" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">阅读文档</a>`,"Choose `agent: add context server`.":"选择“agent：添加上下文服务器”。 (`agent: add context server`)","Click the button below to automatically install in Cursor.":`点击下方的Button即可自动安装到Cursor中。`,"Color Picker for daisyUI":`daisyUI 的颜色选择器`,"Copy/Paste as > Copy link to selection":`复制/粘贴为 > 将 Link 复制到选择`,"Create or edit `opencode.json` in your project root and add the Blueprint MCP configuration.":"在项目根目录中创建或编辑`opencode.json`并添加 Blueprint MCP 配置。","Customer Support":`客户支持`,"daisyUI Color Picker":`daisyUI 颜色选择器`,"daisyUI Laravel":`daisyUI Laravel`,"daisyUI Name":`daisyUI 名称`,'daisyUI name must be written as "daisyUI" with a lowercase "d" and uppercase "UI" with no spaces.':`daisyUI 名称必须写为“daisyUI”，其中包含小写“d”和大写“UI”，且不带空格。`,"daisyUI Pro Components":`daisyUI Pro Components`,"daisyUI Store":`daisyUI商店`,'daisyUI supports the <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-typography" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">TailwindCSS Typography plugin</a>':`daisyUI 支持 <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-typography" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">TailwindCSS Typography 插件</a>`,"Do not use the daisyUI name or logo in a way that suggests your product or service is officially affiliated with, endorsed by, or produced by daisyUI.":`使用 daisyUI 名称或徽标时不得暗示您的产品或服务正式隶属于 daisyUI、由 daisyUI 认可或由 daisyUI 生产。`,'Enable a theme using <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>data-theme</code></a> on your `<html>` tag:':'在 `<html>` 标记上使用 <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#enable-a-built-in-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>data-theme</code></a> 启用主题：',"environment variable for the Blueprint MCP server.":`Blueprint MCP 服务器的环境变量。`,'Every part of daisyUI is <a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@5/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">available on CDN</a> as separate CSS files.':`daisyUI 的每个部分都作为单独的 CSS 文件<a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@5/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">在 CDN 上提供</a>。`,"Exception: daisyUI package stays lower case `daisyui` as it is a package name and must follow coding conventions.":"例外：daisyUI 包保持小写`daisyui`，因为它是包名称，并且必须遵循编码约定。","file_content:read":`文件内容：已读`,"file_dev_resources:read":`file_dev_resources：读取`,"file_metadata:read":`文件元数据：读取`,'For a more efficient daisyUI generation and on-demand component snippets, use <a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI Blueprint MCP server</a>. Blueprint MCP saves more tokens and has more control over the generated code.':`要更高效地生成 daisyUI 和按需 Component 代码段，请使用 <a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI 蓝图 MCP 服务器</a>。 Blueprint MCP 节省了更多令牌，并且对生成的代码有更多控制权。`,'For pagination, we use <a href="/components/join/">join component</a> to show multiple links or buttons next to each other.':`对于 Pagination，我们使用 <a href="/components/join/">join Component</a> 来显示多个彼此相邻的链接或按钮。`,'Get a <a href="/blueprint/checkout/">Blueprint license key</a>.':`获取<a href="/blueprint/checkout/">蓝图许可证密钥</a>。`,'Get a <a href="/blueprint/checkout/">Blueprint License</a>':`获取<a href="/blueprint/checkout/">蓝图许可证</a>`,'Here\'s a React example to save checkbox state in local storage: <a href="https://stackblitz.com/edit/react-checkbox-localstorage?file=src%2FApp.js" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Stackblitz</a>':`下面是一个在本地存储中保存复选框状态的 React 示例： <a href="https://stackblitz.com/edit/react-checkbox-localstorage?file=src%2FApp.js" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Stackblitz</a>`,'If you already use <a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI Blueprint MCP server</a>, you don\'t need to install this plugin.':`如果您已经使用<a href="/blueprint/">daisyUI Blueprint MCP服务器</a>，则无需安装此插件。`,'If you don\'t want to use this feature, <a href="/docs/config/#exclude">you can exclude <code>rootscrollgutter</code></a>.':`如果您不想使用此功能，<a href="/docs/config/#exclude">您可以排除<code>rootscrollgutter</code></a>。`,'If you really need `@tailwindcss/forms` alongside with daisyUI (which I doubt, because both are doing the same job) consider using its <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-forms#using-only-global-styles-or-only-classes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>strategy: \'class\'</code> config</a> so it only applies style to the elements with specific class name (not all form elements)':`如果您确实需要 \`@tailwindcss/forms\` 和 daisyUI （我对此表示怀疑，因为两者都在做相同的工作），请考虑使用其 <a href="https://github.com/tailwindlabs/tailwindcss-forms#using-only-global-styles-or-only-classes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>strategy: 'class'</code> 配置</a>，这样它只将样式应用于具有特定Class name（并非所有表单元素）`,'If you really want to use Tailwind\'s `dark:` variant, <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-apply-tailwinds-dark-selector-for-specific-themes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">here\'s how to do it</a>.':'如果您确实想使用 Tailwind 的 `dark:` 变体，<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-apply-tailwinds-dark-selector-for-specific-themes" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">以下是操作方法</a>。','If you want the collapsed content to be searcheable in browser use the <a href="#-collapse-using-details-and-summary-tag">Collapse using details and summary tag</a>':`如果您希望在浏览器中搜索折叠内容，请使用<a href="#-collapse-using-details-and-summary-tag">使用详细信息和摘要标签折叠</a>`,'If you want the collapsed content to be searcheable in browser use the <a href="#accordion-using-details">Accordion using details</a>':`如果您希望在浏览器中可以搜索折叠的内容，请使用<a href="#accordion-using-details">手风琴使用详细信息</a>`,'If you\'re using <a href="/docs/config/#prefix">daisyUI prefix</a>, it will add prefix to `theme-controller` class.':'如果您使用 <a href="/docs/config/#prefix">daisyUI 前缀</a>，它将向 `theme-controller` 类添加前缀。','If you\'re using <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/styling-with-utility-classes#using-the-prefix-option" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS prefix</a>, it won\'t add prefix to `theme-controller` class.':'如果您使用 <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/styling-with-utility-classes#using-the-prefix-option" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS 前缀</a>，它不会向 `theme-controller` 类添加前缀。','If you\'re using a custom theme make sure you\'re using <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-add-a-new-custom-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">all the required CSS variables</a>':`如果您使用自定义主题，请确保使用<a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/themes/#how-to-add-a-new-custom-theme" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">所有必需的 CSS 变量</a>`,"in Claude Desktop.":`in Claude Desktop.`,"In Cursor press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P, search for `MCP: Open MCP Settings`, and add this configuration to `mcp.json`:":"在 Cursor 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P，或 Ctrl + Shift + P，搜索“MCP：打开 MCP 设置”，并将此配置添加到`MCP: Open MCP Settings`： (`mcp.json`)","In Figma, go to":`在 Figma 中，转到`,"In Figma, right click on a section and choose":`在 Figma 中，右键单击一个部分并选择`,"In your editor, paste the link and ask the LLM to generate daisyUI code for that design.":`在编辑器中，粘贴 Link 并要求 LLM 为该设计生成 daisyUI 代码。`,'Inputs can be used with `validator` class to have validation styles. <a href="/components/validator/">See Validator component</a> for more details.':'输入可以与`validator`类一起使用以具有验证样式。 <a href="/components/validator/">请参阅验证器组件</a>了解更多详细信息。',"Install Codex CLI if you haven't already.":`如果尚未安装 Codex CLI，请安装。`,'Install Elixir according to the <a href="https://elixir-lang.org/install.html" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">official Elixir documentation</a>':`根据<a href="https://elixir-lang.org/install.html" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Elixir 官方文档</a>安装 Elixir`,"Install OpenCode CLI if you haven't already.":`如果尚未安装 OpenCode CLI，请安装。`,"library_assets:read":`图书馆资产：已读`,"library_content:read":`图书馆内容：已读`,'Make sure you\'re not using <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#dynamic-class-names" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">dynamic class names</a> (half-variable like `btn-{$color}`). If you do this, there is no way for Tailwind CSS to find your class names.':'确保您没有使用<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#dynamic-class-names" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">动态类名称</a>（半变量，如`btn-{$color}`）。如果您这样做，Tailwind CSS 将无法找到您的类名。',"My Orders":`我的订单`,"My Orders (old panel)":`我的订单（旧面板）`,"My Project: Built with daisyUI":`我的项目：用daisyUI构建`,"Next: Setup the Figma API":`下一步：设置 Figma API`,"Official daisyUI Extension":`官方 daisyUI 扩展`,"On the MCP settings page, set:":`在MCP设置页面上，设置：`,"Open the Antigravity MCP config file at `~/.gemini/config/mcp_config.json`.":"Open the Antigravity MCP config file at `~/.gemini/config/mcp_config.json`.",'Opening a drawer adds a <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> to the page to avoid layout shift on operating systems that have a fixed scrollbar.':`打开抽屉会向页面添加 <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> ，以避免在具有固定滚动条的操作系统上发生布局变化。`,'Opening a modal adds a <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> to the page to avoid layout shift on operating systems that have a fixed scrollbar.':`打开 Modal 会在页面中添加 <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/scrollbar-gutter" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">scrollbar-gutter</a> ，以避免在具有固定滚动条的操作系统上发生布局变化。`,"Option 1: Automatic setup":`选项 1：自动设置`,"Option 2: Manual setup":`选项 2：手动设置`,"Please do not modify, distort, or alter the logo.":`请勿修改、扭曲或更改徽标。`,"Privacy Policy":`隐私政策`,'React Day Picker is a flexible date picker component for React. <a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read the docs</a>':`React Day Picker 是 React 的灵活日期选择器 Component。 <a href="https://github.com/gpbl/react-day-picker" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">阅读文档</a>`,'Read <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">VS Code docs</a> for more info about using MCP.':`有关使用 MCP 的详细信息，请阅读 <a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">VS Code 文档</a>。`,'Read <a href="https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/claude-code/mcp" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Claude Code docs</a> for more info about using MCP.':`Read <a href="https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/claude-code/mcp" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Claude Code docs</a> for more info about using MCP.`,"Required permissions:":`所需权限：`,"Run this command to add the Blueprint MCP server.":`运行此命令以添加 Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"Run this command to add the Blueprint MCP server. Figma API Key is optional and only needed for Figma-to-code conversion.":`运行此命令以添加 Blueprint MCP 服务器。 Figma API 密钥是可选的，仅在 Figma 到代码转换时需要。`,'Safari has a <a href="https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22261" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">CSS bug</a> since 2008 that prevents button elements from being focused, so we use div `tabindex="0"` as a workaround.':'自 2008 年以来，Safari 就有一个 <a href="https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22261" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">CSS bug</a>，导致 Button 元素无法获得焦点，因此我们使用 div `tabindex="0"` 作为解决方法。',"Search for `MCP: Open User Configuration`.":"搜索“MCP：开放用户配置”。 (`MCP: Open User Configuration`)","Search for `Windsurf: MCP Configuration Panel`.":"搜索“Windsurf：MCP 配置面板”。 (`Windsurf: MCP Configuration Panel`)","Set the Figma API token in the":`在中设置 Figma API 令牌`,"Settings > Security > Personal Access Tokens > Generate new token":`设置 > 安全 > 个人访问令牌 > 生成新令牌`,'So you can use `bg-primary`, `border-secondary`, etc. Read more about <a href="/docs/utilities/">daisyUI color utility classes</a>.':'因此，您可以使用 `bg-primary`、`border-secondary` 等。了解有关 <a href="/docs/utilities/">daisyUI 颜色实用程序类</a>的更多信息。','Some uncommon Tailwind CSS color utility classes for daisyUI colors are available on additional CSS files for CDN usage, see <a href="/docs/colors/#how-to-use">colors docs</a> for more info.':`一些不常见的用于 daisyUI 颜色的 Tailwind CSS 颜色实用程序类可在用于 CDN 使用的其他 CSS 文件上使用，请参阅<a href="/docs/colors/#how-to-use">颜色文档</a>了解更多信息。`,"Step 1: Get a Figma Access Token":`第 1 步：获取 Figma 访问令牌`,"Step 1: License key":`第 1 步：许可证密钥`,"Step 2: Add the token to Blueprint MCP":`步骤 2：将令牌添加到 Blueprint MCP`,"Step 2: Configure MCP settings":`步骤 2：配置 MCP 设置`,"Step 2: Install Codex CLI":`第 2 步：安装 Codex CLI`,"Step 2: Install OpenCode CLI":`第 2 步：安装 OpenCode CLI`,"Step 3: Configure MCP settings":`步骤 3：配置 MCP 设置`,"Step 3: Copy a Figma selection link":`步骤 3：复制 Figma 选择 Link`,"Step 4: Ask your editor to generate daisyUI code":`第 4 步：要求编辑器生成 daisyUI 代码`,"team_library_content:read":`team_library_content：已读`,"Terms and Conditions":`条款和条件`,"Theme Generator made with daisyUI":`使用 daisyUI 制作的主题生成器`,'To setup Tailwind CSS syntax support and IntelliSense, see <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/editor-setup" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS docs</a>.':`要设置 Tailwind CSS syntax 支持和 IntelliSense，请参阅 <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/editor-setup" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS 文档</a>。`,'Try using `@source` <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#explicitly-registering-sources" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Explicitly register sources</a>':'尝试使用 `@source` <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#explicitly-registering-sources" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">显式注册源</a>',"Unofficial daisyUI datepicker":`非官方 daisyUI 日期选择器`,'Using Tailwind CSS and daisyUI, it is expected for CSS files to be very small. Ideally only the class names you used must be in the CSS file. Sometimes (specially in monorepos) it is possible that <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS automatic class name detection</a> finds some unwanted strings in your project and generate styles for them. To avoid this, you can <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#disabling-automatic-detection" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">disable automatic detection</a> and register your source files using `@source` directive.':'使用 Tailwind CSS 和 daisyUI，预计 CSS 文件会非常小。理想情况下，CSS 文件中必须只有您使用的 Class name。有时（特别是在 monorepos 中）<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Tailwind CSS 自动 Class name 检测</a> 可能会在项目中找到一些不需要的字符串并为它们生成样式。为了避免这种情况，您可以<a href="https://tailwindcss.com/docs/detecting-classes-in-source-files#disabling-automatic-detection" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">禁用自动检测</a>并使用`@source`指令注册源文件。','Vanilla Calendar Pro is a JavaScript calendar library. <a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read the docs</a>':`Vanilla Calendar Pro 是一个 JavaScript 日历库。 <a href="https://github.com/uvarov-frontend/vanilla-calendar-pro" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">阅读文档</a>`,'We recommend using an <a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP server</a> for daisyUI.':`我们建议为 daisyUI 使用 <a href="/docs/mcp/">MCP 服务器</a>。`,'When naming your projects, tools, or services, use "for daisyUI" or "compatible with daisyUI" instead of including "daisyUI" at the beginning of your product name.':`命名您的项目、工具或服务时，请使用“for daisyUI”或“与 daisyUI 兼容”，而不是在产品名称的开头包含“daisyUI”。`,'With daisyUI, you don\'t need to manually set colors using <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>dark:</code> variant</a>':`使用 daisyUI，您无需使用 <a href="https://daisyui.com/docs/colors/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank"><code>dark:</code> 变体</a> 手动设置颜色`,'You can also use the native HTML `<input type="date">` for a date picker. <a href="/components/input/#date-input">Read more</a>':'您还可以使用原生 HTML `<input type="date">` 作为日期选择器。 <a href="/components/input/#date-input">了解更多</a>','You can create a dedicated `Workspace` where you can upload the `llms.txt` file. To download the file, visit <a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://daisyui.com/llms.txt</a>, right-click, and select "Save As...". Once downloaded, upload the file as an attachment in the Grok Workspace.':'您可以创建一个专用的“工作区”，您可以在其中上传`Workspace`文件。要下载该文件，请访问 <a href="https://daisyui.com/llms.txt" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://daisyui.com/llms.txt</a>，右键单击，然后 Select“另存为...”。下载后，将文件作为附件上传到 Grok 工作区。 (`llms.txt`)',"You can download the daisyUI logo in SVG and PNG formats for appropriate usage.":`您可以下载 SVG 和 PNG 格式的 daisyUI 徽标以供适当使用。`,'You can setup daisyUI\'s llms.txt file to your workspace so Copilot can use it by default. (<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/overview" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read more at VSCode docs</a>)':`您可以将 daisyUI 的 llms.txt 文件设置到您的工作区，以便 Copilot 可以通过 Default 使用它。 （<a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/copilot/customization/overview" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">在 VSCode 文档中了解更多信息</a>）`,'You can setup daisyUI\'s llms.txt file to your workspace so Cursor can use it by default. (<a href="https://docs.cursor.com/context/rules" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Read more at Cursor docs</a>)':`您可以将 daisyUI 的 llms.txt 文件设置到您的工作区，以便 Cursor 可以通过 Default 使用它。 （<a href="https://docs.cursor.com/context/rules" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">在 Cursor 文档中了解更多信息</a>）`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude Code.':`You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude Code.`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude desktop.':`You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Claude desktop.`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Cline.':`您可以使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作为 Cline 中的 MCP 服务器。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Cursor.':`您可以使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作为 Cursor 中的 MCP 服务器。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in VSCode.':`您可以使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作为 VSCode 中的 MCP 服务器。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Windsurf.':`您可以使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作为 Windsurf 中的 MCP 服务器。`,'You can use <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> or <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> as MCP server in Zed.':`您可以使用 <a href="https://context7.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Context7</a> 或 <a href="https://gitmcp.io/saadeghi/daisyui" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">daisyUI GitMCP</a> 作为 Zed 中的 MCP 服务器。`,"Discount code":`折扣码`,"Limited time discount code":`限时优惠码`,"code at checkout to get":`结帐时获取代码`,"discount.":`折扣。`,"Remaining time":`剩余时间`,Convert:i,"Install guide":`安装指南`,"Get the license":`获得许可证`,"Figma API to LLM":`Figma API 转 LLM`,"I will do my best to help you.":`我会尽力帮助你。`,"What happens after I pay?":`我付款后会发生什么？`,"Will I receive updates?":`我会收到更新吗？`,"Do I get customer support?":`我可以获得客户支持吗？`,"Can I cancel my subscription?":`我可以取消订阅吗？`,"Can I get a refund?":`我可以获得退款吗？`,"I didn't receive the email":`我没有收到电子邮件`,"I bought the wrong package":`我买错了包`,"There was an issue with the payment":`付款出现问题`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Antigravity":`Install Blueprint MCP for Antigravity`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Antigravity.":`Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Antigravity.`,"After configuring the server, tell the AI model to use Blueprint MCP.":`配置服务器后，告诉 AI 模型使用 Blueprint MCP。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Desktop":`Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Desktop`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Desktop.":`Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Desktop.`,"Go to Settings > Developer in Claude Desktop.":`Go to Settings > Developer in Claude Desktop.`,"Click the Edit Config button.":`单击编辑配置 Button。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Code":`Install Blueprint MCP for Claude Code`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Code.":`Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Claude Code.`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Cline":`安装 Cline 蓝图 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Cline.":`为 Cline 安装 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"Select the Configure tab.":`Select 配置选项卡。`,"Click the Configure MCP Servers button at the bottom of the pane.":`单击窗格底部的配置 MCP 服务器 Button。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Codex":`安装 Codex 蓝图 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Codex.":`安装 Codex 的 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Cursor":`为 Cursor 安装蓝图 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Cursor.":`为 Cursor 安装 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"Setup Figma API for Blueprint MCP":`为 Blueprint MCP 设置 Figma API`,"Generate daisyUI code from a Figma design file":`从 Figma 设计文件生成 daisyUI 代码`,"In Figma, go to Settings > Security > Personal Access Tokens > Generate new token.":`在 Figma 中，转到设置 > 安全 > 个人访问令牌 > 生成新令牌。`,"Set the Figma API token in the FIGMA environment variable for the Blueprint MCP server.":`在 Blueprint MCP 服务器的 FigMA 环境变量中设置 Figma API 令牌。`,"In Figma, right click on a section and choose Copy/Paste as > Copy link to selection.":`在 Figma 中，右键单击某个部分并选择复制/粘贴为 > 将 Link 复制到所选内容。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for OpenClaw":`安装 OpenClaw 的 Blueprint MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for OpenClaw.":`为 OpenClaw 安装 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for OpenCode":`安装 Blueprint MCP for OpenCode`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for OpenCode.":`安装适用于 OpenCode 的 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for VSCode Copilot":`安装适用于 VSCode Copilot 的 Blueprint MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for VSCode Copilot.":`为 VSCode Copilot 安装 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"In VS Code press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P.":`在 VS Code 中，按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P 或 Ctrl + Shift + P。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Windsurf":`为 Windsurf 安装蓝图 MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Windsurf.":`为 Windsurf 安装 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"Press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P.":`按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P 或 Ctrl + Shift + P。`,"Click Add custom server +.":`单击添加自定义服务器 +。`,"Install Blueprint MCP for Zed":`安装适用于 Zed 的 Blueprint MCP`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Zed.":`为 Zed 安装 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"In Zed press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P, or Ctrl + Shift + P.":`在 Zed 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P 或 Ctrl + Shift + P。`,"Branding and logo usage guidelines for daisyUI":`daisyUI 的品牌和徽标使用指南`,'To close the dropdown after click, you can use something like `onclick="document.activeElement.blur()"`. <a href="https://play.tailwindcss.com/pc8zXb89lM" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Example</a>':'要在单击后关闭 Dropdown，您可以使用类似 `onclick="document.activeElement.blur()"` 的方法。 <a href="https://play.tailwindcss.com/pc8zXb89lM" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">示例</a>',"Press F to pay respects.":`按F表示敬意。`,"Press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P. Or if it's Windows, press ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P.":`按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P。或者如果是 Windows，请按 ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P。`,"In Cursor press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P ( Or Ctrl + Shift + P )":`在 Cursor 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P （或 Ctrl + Shift + P ）`,"In VS Code press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P ( Or Ctrl + Shift + P )":`在 VS Code 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P （或 Ctrl + Shift + P ）`,"Press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P (or ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P on Windows)":`按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P（或在 Windows 上按 ⌃ Ctrl + ⇧ Shift + P）`,"In Zed press ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P ( Or Ctrl + Shift + P )":`在 Zed 中按 ⌘ CMD + ⇧ Shift + P （或 Ctrl + Shift + P ）`,"Open Cursor settings with ⌘ + ,":`使用 ⌘ + 打开 Cursor 设置，`,"daisyUI community articles":`daisyUI 社区文章`,"Tailwind CSS articles and daisyUI tutorials":`Tailwind CSS 文章和 daisyUI 教程`,"daisyUI community courses":`daisyUI 社区课程`,"Free Tailwind CSS courses and best Tailwind CSS tutorials":`免费 Tailwind CSS 课程和最佳 Tailwind CSS 教程`,"daisyUI community videos":`daisyUI 社区视频`,"Best Tailwind CSS video tutorials and Free Tailwind CSS video courses":`最佳 Tailwind CSS 视频教程和免费 Tailwind CSS 视频课程`,"Official daisyUI Skills":`官方daisyUI技能`,"Enough with AI slop":`受够了 AI slop`,"Setup your coding agent to generate better UI.":`设置 coding agent 以生成更好的 UI。`,"Compatible with all coding agents":`与所有coding agents兼容`,"Coming soon…":`即将推出…`,"daisyUI Skills":`daisyUI技能`,"daisyUI Skills - Tailwind CSS Skill":`daisyUI Skills - Tailwind CSS Skill`,"daisyUI and Tailwind CSS theme generator":`daisyUI 和 Tailwind CSS 主题生成器`,"Tailwind CSS Theme Generator for daisyUI - Custom Tailwind CSS themes with light mode and dark mode support":`Tailwind CSS Theme Generator for daisyUI - 自定义 Tailwind CSS 主题，支持浅色模式和深色模式`,"Sales volume reached $12,450 this week, showing a 15% increase from the previous period.":`本周销量达到 12,450 美元，较上期增长 15%。`,Size:a,"Click the MCP Servers icon at the top navigation bar of the Cline pane.":`Click the MCP Servers icon at the top navigation bar of the Cline pane.`,"Select the  tab.":`Select the  tab.`,"Click the  button at the bottom of the pane.":`Click the  button at the bottom of the pane.`,"After configuring the server, tell the AI model to .":`After configuring the server, tell the AI model to .`,"Go to  in Claude Desktop.":`Go to  in Claude Desktop.`,"Click the  button.":`Click the  button.`,"Click .":`Click .`,"install-btn":`install-btn`,"MCP server":`MCP server`,day:`day`,hour:s,min:`min`,sec:`sec`,Use:`Use`,copied:d,copy:f,close:p,and:`and`,"to daisyUI":`to daisyUI`,"Compatible with":`Compatible with`,"and more":`and more`,"Design System":`Design System`,Resources:h,Solution:g,Providing:_,context:v,It:`It`,Introducing:b,"for daisyUI":`for daisyUI`,variants:x,variables:S,"to generate daisyUI code":`to generate daisyUI code`,"Generate daisyUI code":`Generate daisyUI code`,"daisyUI Blueprint MCP server":`daisyUI Blueprint MCP server`,Examples:C,"Blueprint free trial":`Blueprint 免费试用`,"3-day free trial":`3 天免费试用`,", cancel anytime.":`，可随时取消。`,"Get Your Blueprint License":`获取你的 Blueprint License`,"This page was made with Blueprint MCP and GPT 5.6":`此页面由 Blueprint MCP 和 GPT 5.6 制作`,"The Official":`The Official`,"UI Generator":`UI Generator`,"Creative Director":`Creative Director`,"Page Architect":`Page Architect`,"Design System Expert":`Design System Expert`,"MCP Server":`MCP 服务器`,"The most powerful agentic UI workflow in an MCP server":`MCP 服务器中最强大的 agentic UI workflow`,"10× better code quality":`代码质量提升 10 倍`,"10× faster results":`结果快 10 倍`,"90% lower token costs":`token 成本降低 90%`,"Provides on-demand, fine-tuned UI design knowledge to your AI agent":`为你的 AI 代理按需提供精调的 UI 设计知识`,"After purchase, your license key arrives by email.":`购买后，license 密钥会通过电子邮件发送给你。`,"Install the MCP server, add the key, and ask your agent to use Blueprint.":`安装 MCP 服务器，添加密钥，并要求你的代理使用 Blueprint。`,"One-shots generated by daisyUI Blueprint MCP":`由 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 生成的一次成型作品`,"Interface examples":`界面示例`,"Blueprint MCP server works with coding agents":`Blueprint MCP 服务器可与coding agents配合使用`,"ALL WEBSITES LOOK THE SAME":`所有网站看起来都一样`,"Sick of":`厌倦了`,"AI slop?":`AI slop?`,"AI-generated sites arrive with outdated dependencies, stale syntax, copy-paste layouts, the same color palettes, purple gradients, inconsistent spacing, and a structure so mediocre that no one wants to use it.":`AI 生成的网站往往带着过时依赖、陈旧语法、复制粘贴式布局、相同的配色、紫色渐变、不一致的间距，以及平庸到没人想用的结构。`,"Example of a generic AI-generated landing page":`通用 AI 生成落地页示例`,"The most mediocre layout":`最平庸的布局`,"Boring, inauthentic color palette":`无聊且不真实的配色`,"Looks like every other AI-generated site":`看起来像其他所有 AI 生成网站`,"Inconsistent components, no design system":`组件不一致，没有设计系统`,"Inaccessible, inefficient, and unmaintainable code":`不可访问、低效且难维护的代码`,"AI slop content and lack of structure":`AI slop 内容和结构缺失`,"Purple gradients everywhere":`到处都是紫色渐变`,"TRYING TO FIX THE SLOP WITH INSTRUCTIONS?":`想用指令修复这些垃圾？`,"Your LLM ignores the instructions and skills.":`你的 LLM 会忽略指令和技能。`,"Agent skills are collections of instructions and rules. Check the logs and the pattern is familiar: the model reads a few files, skips the rest, ignores inconvenient rules, and moves on.":`代理技能是一组指令和规则。查看日志就会看到熟悉的模式：模型读几个文件，跳过其余文件，忽略麻烦的规则，然后继续。`,"UI work needs more context than most tasks. Yet as the instruction set grows, the chance of selective reading grows with it.":`UI 工作比大多数任务需要更多 context。但指令集越大，选择性阅读的概率也越高。`,"Skill files inspected":`已检查的技能文件`,"Ignored 40% of the rules":`忽略了 40% 的规则`,"Skipped 23 files due to overconfidence":`因过度自信跳过 23 个文件`,"Ignored the rules and treated them as suggestions only":`忽略规则，只把它们当作建议`,read:w,"Lines 1 to 120":`第 1 到 120 行`,"partially ignored":`部分忽略`,skipped:T,"The model continued without following the rules it was expected to follow.":`模型没有遵守应当遵守的规则就继续了。`,"Wasted time, wasted effort, wasted tokens":`浪费时间，浪费精力，浪费 token`,"Tired of wasting tokens?":`厌倦浪费 token 了吗？`,"Without clear instructions, AI creates the same generic UI for everyone. That's why trends like purple buttons and gradients quickly became overused.":`没有清晰指令时，AI 会为每个人创建同样的通用 UI。这就是紫色按钮和渐变等趋势很快被滥用的原因。`,"Making the design unique takes many prompts, additional edits, wasted time, and LOTS of tokens.":`之后再让设计变得独特，就需要大量提示词、额外修改、浪费时间和大量 token。`,"What if...":`如果……`,"you could one-shot a unique, original, and functional UI without any effort?":`你可以毫不费力地一次生成独特、原创且可用的 UI？`,"No slop. No skip. No waste.":`无垃圾。无跳过。无浪费。`,"Meet the Blueprint MCP tools":`认识 Blueprint MCP 工具`,"THE REAL SOLUTION":`真正的解决方案`,"Blueprint fixes that.":`Blueprint 修复了这一点。`,"Introducing a mandatory MCP workflow.":`引入强制 MCP workflow。`,"Every tool has a defined job and a strict execution order. Each tool provides the necessary resources and functionality to your agent. The agent must follow these rules sequentially. It cannot skip steps, invent component syntax, or mark unfinished work as complete.":`每个工具都有明确职责和严格的执行顺序。每个工具都会向你的代理提供必要资源和功能。代理必须按顺序遵守这些规则。它不能跳过步骤、编造组件语法，或把未完成的工作标记为完成。`,"Rules and principles":`规则和原则`,"LLM is forced to read and follow":`LLM 被强制阅读并遵守`,"Page architectures":`页面架构`,"Matched by intent":`按意图匹配`,"daisyUI components":`daisyUI 组件`,"Syntax, examples, code snippets":`语法、示例、代码片段`,"Final inspection":`最终检查`,"Finds and fixes visual issues":`发现并修复视觉问题`,"Convert everything to daisyUI.":`把所有内容转换为 daisyUI。`,"Blueprint gives your agent the tools to understand the source first. It extracts the structure, chooses the matching daisyUI components, supplies exact snippets, and checks the conversion when the code is done.":`Blueprint 先给你的代理理解源内容的工具。它提取结构，选择匹配的 daisyUI 组件，提供精确片段，并在代码完成后检查转换结果。`,"Figma converts to daisyUI":`Figma 转换为 daisyUI`,"Tailwind CSS converts to daisyUI":`Tailwind CSS 转换为 daisyUI`,"Screenshot converts to daisyUI":`截图转换为 daisyUI`,Screenshot:E,"Bootstrap converts to daisyUI":`Bootstrap 转换为 daisyUI`,"Image palette converts to daisyUI":`图片调色板转换为 daisyUI`,"Image color palette":`图片调色板`,"Picture color palette to a daisyUI theme":`图片调色板转换为 daisyUI 主题`,"See Blueprint in action":`观看 Blueprint 实际运行`,"Watch Blueprint's MCP server create unique, authentic UIs from a simple prompt. The server gives your AI agent the context it needs: design-system principles, code snippets, and UX direction. When the page is finished, Blueprint inspects the code and fixes visual issues.":`观看 Blueprint 的 MCP 服务器如何从一个简单提示词创建独特、真实的 UI。服务器会给你的 AI 代理所需的 context：设计系统原则、代码片段和 UX 方向。页面完成后，Blueprint 会检查代码并修复视觉问题。`,"Blueprint MCP server converts a Figma design to daisyUI":`Blueprint MCP 服务器将 Figma 设计转换为 daisyUI`,"Blueprint MCP server converts Tailwind CSS to daisyUI":`Blueprint MCP 服务器将 Tailwind CSS 转换为 daisyUI`,"COMPARE WITH OTHER OPTIONS":`与其他选项比较`,"All-in-one.":`一体化。`,"Documentation context helps an LLM answer questions. Blueprint surrounds that official source with project setup, creative direction, page architecture, exact component retrieval, conversion workflows, and a final inspection gate.":`文档 context 能帮助 LLM 回答问题。Blueprint 在这份official来源之外加入项目设置、创意方向、页面架构、精确组件检索、转换 workflows 和最终检查关卡。`,"Comparison of daisyUI Blueprint MCP, daisyUI Skill, Context7 MCP, and GitMCP":`daisyUI Blueprint MCP、daisyUI 技能、Context7 MCP 和 GitMCP 对比`,"Need something else? Email":`还需要别的？发送邮件`,"and we will help.":`我们会帮忙。`,"The official daisyUI MCP server":`official daisyUI MCP 服务器`,"Your license key arrives by email.":`你的 license 密钥会通过电子邮件发送。`,"Add it to the MCP server and ask your coding agent to use Blueprint.":`将它添加到 MCP 服务器，并要求你的编码代理使用 Blueprint。`,"v1.5":`v1.5`,"July 2026":`2026 年 7 月`,"Blueprint now helps your LLM generate the whole UI, not only individual components.":`Blueprint 现在帮助你的 LLM 生成整个 UI，而不只是单个组件。`,"MCP tools":`MCP 工具`,"New: daisyUI Setup Expert. Knows how to set up and configure daisyUI, themes, fonts, and icons.":`新增：daisyUI 设置专家。了解如何设置和配置 daisyUI、主题、字体和图标。`,"New: daisyUI Rules Enforcer. Enforces the rules and principles.":`新增：daisyUI Rules Enforcer。强制执行规则和原则。`,"New: daisyUI Creative Director. Provides a design trends catalog, UX principles, creative decisions, and taste.":`新增：daisyUI Creative Director。提供设计趋势目录、UX 原则、创意决策和品味。`,"New: daisyUI Page Architect. Knows how to structure pages and layouts, what content they need, and which components to use.":`新增： daisyUI Page Architect.了解如何组织页面和布局、需要哪些内容以及使用哪些组件。`,"Updated: daisyUI Component Syntax Expert. Provides exact code syntax, daisyUI snippets, and examples.":`更新：daisyUI Component Syntax Expert。提供精确代码语法、daisyUI 片段和示例。`,"New: daisyUI Quality Inspector. Checks design and code quality, then requires the LLM to fix any issues.":`新增：daisyUI Quality Inspector。检查设计和代码质量，然后要求 LLM 修复所有问题。`,"Updated: Figma to daisyUI. Improved Figma conversion.":`更新：Figma to daisyUI。改进 Figma 转换。`,Prompts:D,"The Tailwind CSS, Bootstrap, and Screenshot to daisyUI prompts, plus Image to daisyUI theme, are now available as MCP tools. MCP clients that don't support MCP prompts can use them too.":`Tailwind CSS、Bootstrap、截图转 daisyUI 的提示词，以及图片转 daisyUI 主题，现在都可作为 MCP 工具使用。不支持 MCP 提示词的 MCP 客户端也能使用它们。`,"MCP resources":`MCP 资源`,"Updated: Snippet":`更新：代码片段`,"New: Setup":`新增：设置`,"New: Rule":`新增：规则`,"New: Page":`新增：页面`,"Setup Expert":`设置专家`,Mandatory:O,"Reads the repo first. It understands dependencies, framework, configuration, themes, colors, fonts, icons, and file structure before your agent changes a pixel.":`先读取 repo。它会在你的代理修改任何像素前理解依赖、框架、配置、主题、颜色、字体、图标和文件结构。`,"Your agent gets the daisyUI install instructions, daisyUI config, and daisyUI custom theme setup when needed.":`你的代理会在需要时获得 daisyUI 安装说明、daisyUI 配置和 daisyUI 自定义主题设置。`,"Installing daisyUI":`安装 daisyUI`,"Adding custom theme, fonts and icons":`添加自定义主题、字体和图标`,"Rules Enforcer":`规则执行器`,"Loads implementation, syntax, accessibility, responsive, theme, media, and quality rules as requirements your LLM must follow.":`将实现、语法、可访问性、响应式、主题、媒体和质量规则作为你的 LLM 必须遵守的要求加载。`,"The workflow cannot continue by skimming half a skill file and quietly dropping the difficult constraints.":`workflow 不能只快速浏览半个技能文件，然后悄悄丢掉困难约束就继续。`,"Enforced design rules and code instructions":`已执行设计规则和代码指令`,"Creative direction":`创意方向`,"Directs UX, content, originality, color, composition, typography, imagery, design trends, and motion as one coherent idea.":`把 UX、内容、原创性、颜色、构图、排版、图像、设计趋势和动效作为一个连贯想法来指导。`,"Instead of another purple-gradient template, the page gets a point of view connected to its product and audience.":`页面不会再是另一个紫色渐变模板，而是获得与产品和受众相关的观点。`,"Applied creative design rules":`已应用创意设计规则`,"Applied UI/UX principles":`已应用 UI/UX 原则`,"Applied an appropriate design trend":`已应用合适的设计趋势`,Architecture:k,"Chooses from 211 page architectures covering purpose, structure, content, goals, states, edge cases, and component composition.":`从 211 个页面架构中选择，覆盖目的、结构、内容、目标、状态、边缘情况和组件组合。`,"Your LLM stops guessing what belongs on the page. It gets a production plan shaped around the job the page must do.":`你的 LLM 不再猜页面该有什么。它会得到围绕页面任务塑造的生产计划。`,"Accessing page architecture library":`访问页面架构库`,"Finding the best layout structure":`寻找最佳布局结构`,"Component Syntax Expert":`组件语法专家`,"Retrieves exact, correct daisyUI component structures, variants, code snippets, and examples only when the page needs them.":`仅在页面需要时检索精确、正确的 daisyUI 组件结构、变体、代码片段和示例。`,"No stale syntax from model memory. No utility pile pretending to be a maintained component.":`没有来自模型记忆的陈旧语法。没有把 utility 堆当成受维护组件。`,"Received daisyUI components and rules":`已收到 daisyUI 组件和规则`,"Received code snippets and examples":`已收到代码片段和示例`,"Quality Inspector":`质量检查员`,"Final gate":`最终关卡`,"Audits the finished source for visual problems, syntax errors, accessibility issues, responsive failures, and ignored rules.":`审查完成后的源代码，查找视觉问题、语法错误、可访问性问题、响应式失败和被忽略的规则。`,"When the inspection finds a problem, your agent has to fix it before the workflow can call the page finished.":`当检查发现问题时，你的代理必须修复它，workflow 才能称页面完成。`,"Fixed syntax issues":`已修复语法问题`,"Fixed visual design problems":`已修复视觉设计问题`,"Front-end skill":`前端技能`,"Make an admin dashboard for server management with Retro-Futurism style":`用 Retro-Futurism 风格制作一个服务器管理后台`,"UI skills":`UI 技能`,"Make an email client UI with clean design":`制作一个干净设计的邮件客户端 UI`,"daisyUI skill":`daisyUI 技能`,"Make a dense Japanese news website with Maximalism style":`用 Maximalism 风格制作一个密集的日本新闻网站`,"UI design agent":`UI 设计代理`,"Make a product management dashboard for managing SaaS businesses":`制作一个用于管理 SaaS 业务的产品管理仪表盘`,"Design website with Codex":`用 Codex 设计网站`,"Make an online shop with Skeuomorphism design for selling gaming headphones":`制作一个用于销售游戏耳机的 Skeuomorphism 风格网店`,"AI site maker":`AI 网站生成器`,"Make a landing page for a cute cafe in Seul":`为首尔一家可爱咖啡馆制作落地页`,"Tailwind CSS skill":`Tailwind CSS 技能`,"Make an event website for a dev confrence in Tokyo":`为东京的开发者会议制作活动网站`,"Best UI design skill":`最佳 UI 设计技能`,"Make a Swiss design style landingpage for a nordic style furniture manifacturer":`为北欧风家具制造商制作 Swiss design 风格落地页`,"Front-end agent":`前端代理`,"Make an artistic personal site for a photographer":`为摄影师制作艺术个人网站`,"Figma to daisyUI":`Figma 转 daisyUI`,"Reads frames, hierarchy, auto layout, type, color, component instances, and a rendered preview before matching daisyUI patterns.":`在匹配 daisyUI 模式前读取 frame、层级、auto layout、类型、颜色、组件实例和渲染预览。`,"Tailwind CSS to daisyUI":`Tailwind CSS 转 daisyUI`,"Preserves layout and behavior while replacing hand-built component utility stacks with current daisyUI structures.":`在用当前 daisyUI 结构替换手写组件 utility 堆的同时，保留布局和行为。`,"Screenshot to daisyUI":`截图转 daisyUI`,"Analyzes hierarchy, density, states, and responsive clues, then rebuilds the reference with accessible daisyUI components.":`分析层级、密度、状态和响应式线索，然后用可访问的 daisyUI 组件重建参考。`,"Bootstrap to daisyUI":`Bootstrap 转 daisyUI`,"Maps Bootstrap components to daisyUI while keeping the content, semantics, structure, and interaction model intact.":`将 Bootstrap 组件映射到 daisyUI，同时保持内容、语义、结构和交互模型完整。`,"Image to daisyUI theme":`图片转 daisyUI 主题`,"Extracts an image palette, assigns semantic roles, calculates readable content colors, and generates every required daisyUI theme variable.":`提取图片调色板，分配语义角色，计算可读内容颜色，并生成所有必需的 daisyUI 主题变量。`,"daisyUI <div class='-my-1 inline-grid grid-cols-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] grid-rows-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] align-middle'><div class='border-s border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/1/2/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/3/2/4]'></div><div class='border-s border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/1/4/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/3/4/4]'></div><div class='font-title m-0.5 bg-blue-600 px-1 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-white [grid-area:1/1/4/4]'>BLUEPRINT</div></div> MCP":`daisyUI <div class='-my-1 inline-grid grid-cols-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] grid-rows-[.25rem_1fr_.25rem] align-middle'><div class='border-s border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/1/2/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-t border-blue-600 [grid-area:1/3/2/4]'></div><div class='border-s border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/1/4/2]'></div><div class='border-e border-b border-blue-600 [grid-area:3/3/4/4]'></div><div class='font-title m-0.5 bg-blue-600 px-1 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide text-white [grid-area:1/1/4/4]'>BLUEPRINT</div></div> MCP`,"daisyUI Skill":`daisyUI 技能`,"Context7 MCP":`Context7 MCP`,GitMCP:A,"daisyUI Official":`daisyUI Official`,"Fine-tuned for daisyUI":`为 daisyUI 精调`,"<span class='text-error'>Impossible to fine-tune</span>":`<span class='text-error'>无法精调</span>`,"Data source":`数据来源`,"<span class='text-success'>Authored & verified</span>":`<span class='text-success'>编写并验证</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>AI-generated</span>":`<span class='text-error'>AI 生成</span>`,"Resource accuracy":`资源准确性`,"<span class='text-success'>100% accurate</span>":`<span class='text-success'>100% 准确</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Confuses random repos</span>":`<span class='text-error'>混淆随机 repos</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Confuses random pages</span>":`<span class='text-error'>混淆随机页面</span>`,"Includes unwanted context":`包含不需要的 context`,"<span class='text-success'>No</span>":`<span class='text-success'>否</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Depends on the LLM</span>":`<span class='text-error'>取决于 LLM</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Yes</span>":`<span class='text-error'>是</span>`,"211 page architectures":`211 个页面架构`,"Design trends catalog":`设计趋势目录`,"Code snippets":`代码片段`,"Quality inspection":`质量检查`,"daisyUI design system specs":`daisyUI 设计系统规格`,"Converts Figma to daisyUI":`将 Figma 转换为 daisyUI`,"Converts Tailwind CSS to daisyUI":`将 Tailwind CSS 转换为 daisyUI`,"Converts Bootstrap to daisyUI":`将 Bootstrap 转换为 daisyUI`,"Generates themes from an image":`从图片生成主题`,"Provides component pictures to AI":`向 AI 提供组件图片`,"Generates AI slop":`生成 AI slop`,"<span class='text-success'>Less likely</span>":`<span class='text-success'>可能性更低</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>More likely</span>":`<span class='text-error'>可能性更高</span>`,"<span class='text-success'>Synced with daisyUI</span>":`<span class='text-success'>与 daisyUI 同步</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Depends on a crawler</span>":`<span class='text-error'>取决于爬虫</span>`,"Token usage efficiency":`Token 使用效率`,"<span class='text-success'>Super efficient</span>":`<span class='text-success'>非常高效</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Not efficient</span>":`<span class='text-error'>不高效</span>`,"<span class='text-error'>Wastes tokens on unrelated context</span>":`<span class='text-error'>在无关 context 上浪费 token</span>`,"Is this a one-time payment or a subscription?":`这是一次性付款还是订阅？`,"Both are possible. You can purchase a monthly license, yearly license, or lifetime license.":`两种都可以。你可以购买月度 license、年度 license 或终身 license。`,"You will receive an email with a license key that you can use to activate the MCP server. If you don't see the email, check your spam folder.":`你会收到一封包含 license 密钥的电子邮件，可用于激活 MCP 服务器。如果没有看到邮件，请检查垃圾邮件文件夹。`,"Yes. Blueprint is updated automatically with the latest version of daisyUI. New MCP tools, resources, and prompts are added automatically.":`是的。Blueprint 会自动更新到最新版本的 daisyUI。新的 MCP 工具、资源和 prompt 会自动添加。`,"We offer support via Discord. Join the daisyUI Discord and ask your questions there.":`我们通过 Discord 提供支持。加入 daisyUI Discord 并在那里提问。`,"Open Discord":`打开 Discord`,"Yes. You can cancel at any time from the order portal. You will keep access until the end of your billing cycle.":`是的。你可以随时在订单门户取消。你会保留访问权限直到计费周期结束。`,"Manage orders":`管理订单`,"Digital products are not refundable. If there was a payment mistake, such as a duplicate payment, email us and we will help resolve it.":`数字产品不可退款。如果出现付款错误，例如重复付款，请给我们发邮件，我们会帮助解决。`,"Email help@daisyui.com":`发送邮件至 help@daisyui.com`,"Check your spam folder first. If you still can't find it, email help@daisyui.com.":`请先检查垃圾邮件文件夹。如果仍然找不到，请发送邮件至 help@daisyui.com。`,"Email support":`联系支持`,"Email help@daisyui.com and we will help you get the right package.":`发送邮件至 help@daisyui.com，我们会帮你获得正确的套餐。`,"If the payment failed and you did not receive the product, try again. If money was deducted, it is usually refunded automatically within one or two weeks. Email help@daisyui.com if the issue persists.":`如果付款失败且你没有收到产品，请重试。如果已扣款，通常会在一到两周内自动退款。如果问题仍然存在，请发送邮件至 help@daisyui.com。`,"Step 2: Install Grok Build":`第2步：安装Grok Build`,"Install Grok Build if you haven't already.":`如果尚未安装 Grok Build，请安装。`,"Run this command to add the Blueprint MCP server. The `FIGMA` API key is optional and only needed for Figma-to-code conversion.":"运行此命令以添加 Blueprint MCP 服务器。 `FIGMA` API 密钥是可选的，仅在 Figma-to-code 转换时需要。",'Check the connection with `grok mcp doctor daisyui-blueprint`. Read the <a href="https://docs.x.ai/build/features/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Grok Build MCP docs</a> for project-scoped configuration and troubleshooting.':'检查与 `grok mcp doctor daisyui-blueprint` 的连接。阅读 <a href="https://docs.x.ai/build/features/mcp-servers" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">Grok Build MCP 文档</a> 以了解项目范围的配置和故障排除。',"MADE WITH BLUEPRINT MCP":`使用 Blueprint MCP 制作`,"LLMs often produce generic AI slop by default. They can skim skill files, ignore difficult instructions, hallucinate component syntax, and settle for mediocre design. You then spend more time, effort, and tokens asking for edits.":`默认情况下，LLMs 通常会生成通用 AI 斜率。他们可以浏览技能文件，忽略困难的指令，产生组件语法的幻觉，并满足于平庸的设计。然后你会花费更多的时间、精力和代币来要求编辑。`,"Blueprint solves this with a guided MCP workflow. Six tools walk the LLM through the task, supply rules and resources one step at a time, and confirm the LLM understood them. The LLM then writes the code. A final inspection finds quality problems for the LLM to fix.":`Blueprint 通过指导 MCP 工作流程解决了这个问题。六种工具引导 LLM 完成任务，一次一步地提供规则和资源，并确认 LLM 理解它们。然后 LLM 写入代码。最终检查发现 LLM 存在质量问题需要修复。`,"1. Setup Expert":`1. 设置专家`,"Provides project-specific setup resources:":`提供特定于项目的设置资源：`,"Framework and dependency information":`框架和依赖信息`,"Tailwind CSS and daisyUI installation guidance":`Tailwind CSS 和 daisyUI 安装指南`,"Configuration, themes, colors, fonts, icons, and file structure":`配置、主题、颜色、字体、图标和文件结构`,"This helps the LLM work with your existing project instead of guessing its setup or adding conflicting configuration.":`这有助于 LLM 与您现有的项目配合使用，而不是猜测其设置或添加冲突的配置。`,"2. Rules Enforcer":`2. 规则执行者`,"Provides the complete daisyUI requirements for:":`提供完整的 daisyUI 要求：`,"Component implementation and syntax":`组件实现和语法`,"Accessibility and responsive behavior":`可访问性和响应行为`,"Themes, media, and code quality":`主题、媒体和代码质量`,"This keeps the LLM from skimming the rules or dropping constraints once it starts coding.":`这可以防止 LLM 在开始编码后忽略规则或放弃约束。`,"3. Creative Director":`3.创意总监`,"Provides design guidance for:":`提供设计指导：`,"Product content, audience, and user experience":`产品内容、受众和用户体验`,"Components, icons, images, design trends, and motion":`组件、图标、图像、设计趋势和动作`,"This gives the LLM one clear visual direction. It avoids disconnected choices and familiar AI-generated layouts.":`这为 LLM 提供了一个清晰的视觉方向。它避免了断开连接的选择和熟悉的 AI 生成的布局。`,"4. Page Architect":`4.页面架构师`,"Provides a matching plan from 211 page architectures, including:":`提供211个页面架构的匹配方案，包括：`,"Page purpose, sections, content order, and user goals":`页面用途、部分、内容顺序和用户目标`,"Actions, navigation, and component composition":`操作、导航和组件组合`,"Responsive behavior, interaction states, and edge cases":`响应行为、交互状态和边缘情况`,"This helps the LLM plan the full page before writing markup, including states a short prompt may leave out.":`这有助于 LLM 在编写标记之前规划整个页面，包括简短提示可能遗漏的状态。`,"5. Component Syntax Expert":`5. 组件语法专家`,"Provides current daisyUI resources for each required component:":`为每个所需组件提供当前的 daisyUI 资源：`,"Correct structure and class names":`正确的结构和类名`,"Variants, sizes, states, and modifiers":`变体、尺寸、状态和修饰符`,"Rules, code snippets, and examples":`规则、代码片段和示例`,"This lets the LLM use maintained daisyUI syntax instead of recalling stale or invented classes from training data.":`这使得 LLM 使用维护的 daisyUI 语法，而不是从训练数据中调用陈旧或发明的类。`,"6. Quality Inspector":`6、质检员`,"Checks the finished source for:":`检查完成的源代码：`,"daisyUI syntax and rule violations":`daisyUI 语法和规则违规`,"Visual hierarchy, spacing, density, and composition":`视觉层次、间距、密度和构图`,"Accessibility, responsive behavior, themes, and missing states":`可访问性、响应行为、主题和缺失状态`,"This gives the LLM a specific repair list. The work finishes after the LLM fixes the reported issues and verifies the result.":`这为 LLM 提供了特定的维修列表。 LLM 修复报告的问题并验证结果后，工作完成。`,"Design taste, originality, composition, color, and typography":`设计品味、原创性、构图、色彩和版式`,"Get Blueprint MCP":`获取 Blueprint MCP`,"New and updated tools, prompts, and resources in daisyUI Blueprint v1.5.":`daisyUI Blueprint v1.5 中新增和更新的工具、提示和资源。`,"Install daisyUI Blueprint MCP server for Grok Build.":`为 Grok Build 安装 daisyUI Blueprint MCP 服务器。`,"See how six Blueprint MCP tools give your LLM the resources it needs to build better daisyUI interfaces.":`了解六种 Blueprint MCP 工具如何为您的 LLM 提供构建更好的 daisyUI 接口所需的资源。`};export{k as Architecture,i as Convert,C as Examples,A as GitMCP,b as Introducing,y as It,O as Mandatory,D as Prompts,_ as Providing,r as Randomize,h as Resources,E as Screenshot,t as Server,a as Size,g as Solution,e as Updates,u as Use,m as and,p as close,v as context,d as copied,f as copy,o as day,j as default,s as hour,c as min,w as read,l as sec,T as skipped,n as spacing,S as variables,x as variants};